Your home or building is a significant asset. One reason RubberRoofs consciously works to be The Trusted Name in Waterproofing. RubberRoofs is focused on giving our clients the best possible service, with the best possible results. Get to know us. At RubberRoofs we value good relationships with our clients, employees, suppliers, and communities, through honesty, which builds confidence, trust, and in turn, loyalty. For example, it is important to us to confidently stand by our warranty and if a problem occurs, we prioritize solving it. We have grown from strength to strength and hundreds of homes, complex, commercial, and industrial building owners can attest to our continued trustworthy service. “I wish to extend my gratitude to Donovan and his team. They are great in many ways, their work, skill and respect,” – Malinga-family, Johannesburg. A proudly South African company, RubberRoofs was established to manufacture the best quality Liquid Rubber Paint™ waterproofing solution possible, with teams of RubberRoofs applicators that adhere to high standards.  The Product Successful application of Liquid Rubber Paint™ waterproofing, like all long-lasting applications, needs thorough methods and knowledgeable skills. RubberRoofs applicators understand quality waterproofing. Waterproofing paint formulations differ markedly from one another. The quality of the ingredients and formulations, affect how products perform and remain stable in our harsh African climate. The RubberRoofs factory and development team, work closely under the guidance of a world-renowned laboratory in ensuring the best, benchmarked, proprietary formulations, employing excellent quality ingredients, processes, and practices. RubberRoofs’ Liquid Rubber Paint™ is designed to out-perform both the market and the 10-year product warranty. WATERPROOFING BEFORE & AFTER       Liquid Rubber Paint™ is a proven impermeable waterproof barrier with impeccable water uptake resistance, outstanding UV stability, and real-life resistance to UV aging. Highly adhesive to a variety of roofing substrates, our Liquid Rubber Paint™ has excellent mechanical properties, remaining elastic through a broad range of temperatures and with high stain resistance, while being environmentally conscious.  In our efforts to apply the best waterproofing solution possible, several rare application controls are the norm at RubberRoofs, like the effective sanitizing and preventative treatments we apply to solve algae, moss, and bio-organisms, on all coastal applications. RubberRoofs provides more than just an effective waterproofing solution. Our excellent Liquid Rubber Paint™ provides your home or building with a cost-effective, new lease on life, and a RubberRoofs application significantly improves your property’s value and even marketability. Cool Roof Technology Are you aware of RubberRoofs’ remarkable next-generation cool roof technology? ThermoTech™ substantially impacts the interior comfort of your home or the interior processes of your building. Find out more about ThermoTech™ Cool Roof Technology at www.RubberRoofs.co.za. Hope Again Wellness Centre A pillar of the RubberRoofs company culture is an impactful facet in fulfilling a key part of a redemptive process, employing the unemployable, loving the unlovable. RubberRoofs was established by the same founder of Hope Again Wellness Centre, Frikkie Hefer. Hope Again Wellness Centre, is a multi-site, non-profit, faith-based, rehabilitation organization. Many RubberRoofs employees have received employment after successfully completing the Hope Again Wellness Centre therapeutic program. You are welcome to visit www.harc.co.za